# Design tokens — read-only for the agent

Never modify token source files or files generated from them. Tokens flow from Figma via Tokens Studio; the build pipeline produces code output.

## Do not edit

- `src/tokens/tokens.json` — source of truth, synced from Figma/Tokens Studio
- `src/tokens/variables.css` — auto-generated CSS custom properties
- `src/tokens/colors.ts` — auto-generated TypeScript token exports

These files include an `AUTO-GENERATED` banner. Treat them as read-only.

## Do not edit component CSS to wire tokens

Do not update files like `src/components/*.css` to reference new token variables. The user owns that wiring.

## Allowed changes

- `style-dictionary.config.js` — build pipeline / output format only
- Running `npm run build:tokens` to regenerate output after the user syncs tokens from Figma

## When tokens need to change

1. User updates tokens in Figma and syncs via Tokens Studio → `tokens.json`
2. Run `npm run build:tokens` to regenerate `variables.css` and `colors.ts`
3. User wires component CSS to the new `--ds-comp-*` or `--ds-color-*` variables if needed
